WEBVTT

04:19.842 --> 04:21.010
Bullshit.

07:30.700 --> 07:33.703
Flowers go next door,
please, Isabelle. Oh, my darling!

07:43.671 --> 07:46.257
I didn't go to the market.
Too much to do. So you'll go.

07:47.717 --> 07:48.551
Of course.

07:59.437 --> 08:02.148
It's an American custom
to show off your home to visitors.

08:02.231 --> 08:04.192
Really? Does she want to see our bins too?

08:09.780 --> 08:11.866
I want to show you something
in the office.

08:35.139 --> 08:36.182
You must be Emily.

08:42.396 --> 08:44.023
The champagne father.

11:41.033 --> 11:42.702
And an American, too. Perfect.

12:18.654 --> 12:19.947
To the Queen of <i>Remueurs!</i>

13:53.415 --> 13:54.792
Gérard, serve her.

15:20.836 --> 15:21.921
Just let him be.

19:04.518 --> 19:07.146
<i>...you're ruining my relationship</i>
<i>with Gabriel.</i>

19:07.229 --> 19:10.149
<i>Mom, I'm fed up of you</i>
<i>always trying to control everything!</i>

19:10.232 --> 19:12.651
<i>He's crazy to refuse the money.</i>
<i>It's nonsense!</i>
